mil.nga.giat.geowave.analytic.partitioner

Interface Partitioner<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPartitioner, AdapterBasedPartitioner, OrthodromicDistancePartitioner

    public interface Partitioner<T>
    Provide a partition for a data item. Multiple partitions are permitted. Only one partition is consider primary. A primary partition is the partition for an item in which the item is processed on behalf of itself. All other partitions are those partitions that require visibility to the a specific item for other items to reference. This approach supports nearest neighbor type queries. Consider that an item can only discover neighbors in its partition. However, the item can be discovered as a nearest neighbor in those partitions in which the item participates as a none primary.
